|tab3 = Melnath's Shoulder |category3 = Story Exclusive Enemy |level3 = 8 |area3 = [[Melnath's Shoulder (XC3)|Melnath's Shoulder]] |spawntime3 = Story Event |respawn3 = No }} '''Agnus Attackers''' are enemies in {{XC3}} and {{XC3FR|sublink}}. They are [[Agnus Forces|Agnus Soldiers]], and are fought at level 1 in [[Everblight Plain]] and level 6 - 7 in [[Alfeto Valley]] during Chapter 1. One Agnus Attacker from [[Colony Gamma]] attacks [[Mio]], [[Sena]], and [[Taion]] on orders from Consul [[G]] after the three "deserted" from fighting the war against [[Keves]], while also serving as the "first" enemy to be fought by the player controlling the Agnian trio. {{clr}}
