{{spoiler}} {{Infobox Character |name = Alexandria |image = XC3 Alexandria Portrait Art.png |species = [[Agnus|Agnian]] human |gender = Female |age = 6th Term |haircolor = Brown |eyecolor = Green |affiliation = [[Colony Iota]] |voiceactorjp = [[wikipedia:Ami Koshimizu|Ami Koshimizu]] |voiceactoreng = [https://www.imdb.com/name/nm2477879/ Sharlit Deyzac] |appearances = {{XC3}} }} '''Alexandria''' (Japanese: {{lang|ja|ニイナ }}, ''Nīna'') is a character in {{XC3}}.
== Overview == She can be recruited as a [[Hero]].<ref>https://www.nintendo.co.jp/switch/az3ha/story/index.html</ref> Alexandria is the commander of [[Colony Iota]], and she has got a strong reputation in [[Agnus]] as well as in [[Keves]] for her skillful swordsmanship and strategies like her ability to judge the war situation.<ref>https://twitter.com/XenobladeJP/status/1544940782104223744</ref><ref>https://twitter.com/XenobladeJP/status/1544941904449589248</ref><ref>https://twitter.com/NintendoEurope/status/1544954395577679874</ref> She helped invent the [[Collectopaedia (XC3)|Collectopedia Cards]] as a method of streamlining logistics and gathering intelligence on other colonies.
Alexandria is recruited by completing the [[Hero Quest]] ''[[Her Reasons]]''. Her [[Class Rank (XC3)|Class Rank]] can be increased to 20 by completing the Ascension Quest ''[[Inescapable Past]]''.
== Story ==
== Gameplay == Her [[Class (XC3)|class]] is [[Incursor]], an [[Attacker]] class. She wields a sword-like [[Blade (XC3)|blade]] to cut down [[Enemy (XC3)|enemies]] with her brilliant swordsmanship. Each time she makes a critical hit, her attack power increases, making her stronger and stronger in battle.
Alexandria's [[Chain Attack (XC3)|Chain Art]] is [[Whistling Blades]],<ref>https://twitter.com/XenobladeJP/status/1544940771534462976</ref> and her Heroic Chain bonus gives her TP a 125% modifier as well as making all of her attacks critical if she is the first to act during a Chain Order.
