Alexandria equips the following gems: * [[Steady Striker]] * [[Steelcleaver]], at level 20 onwards * [[Analyze Weakness]], at level 40 onwards
Alexandria equips the following accessories as her default accessories, which can be changed in post-game or [[New Game + (XC3)|New Game+]]. All equipped accessories assume their Common variant. * [[Ice Headband (XC3)|Ice Headband]] * [[Vibrant Armring]], at level 30 onwards * [[Thermo Headgear]], at level 50 onwards {{Clr}}
