== Battle == {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Craftmaiden Alexandria |image = |caption = Craftmaiden Alexandria |category = [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]] |type = [[Agnus Forces]] |level = 41 |area = [[Elaice Highway]] ([[Colony Iota]]) |spawntime = During ''[[Her Reasons]]'' |respawn = No |movement = |exp = |cp = |sp = |gold = |hp = |strength = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate = }} '''Craftmaiden Alexandria''' is a [[Quest Exclusive Enemy (XC3)|Quest Exclusive]] [[Boss (XC3)|Boss]]. She is an [[Agnus Forces|Agnus Soldier]] who is fought at level 41 in [[Colony Iota]] at [[Elaice Highway]] during ''[[Her Reasons]]''. {{clr}}
=== Challenge Battle Mode === {{Infobox XC3 Enemy |name = Craftmaiden Alexandria |image = |caption = Craftmaiden Alexandria |type = [[Agnus Forces]] |movement = Ground |area = [[Land of Challenge (XC3)|Land of Challenge]] |category = [[Challenge Battle Enemy (XC3)|Challenge Battle Boss]] |level = 120 |detection = |spawntime = During ''[[Heroes Frontline]]'' |respawn = No |hp = 3,519,120 |strength = |dexterity = |agility = |physdef = |ethdef = |critrate = |guardrate = }} '''Craftmaiden Alexandria''' is fought at level 120 during the third wave of the [[Challenge Battle Mode|Challenge Battle]] ''[[Heroes Frontline]]''.
{{clr}}
== Etymology == [[wikipedia:Alexandria|Alexandria]] (Greek: Αλεξάνδρεια) is an ancient Greek city in Egypt. It was once home to the [[wikipedia:Library of Alexandria|Library of Alexandria]], one of the largest libraries of the ancient world which acted as a universal collection of all knowledge.
== Trivia == * Alexandria's Japanese voice actress, Ami Koshimizu, also voices [[Perun]] in {{XC2}}. She also provides the "Sultry" female voice for [[Cross]] in {{XCX}}.
